title: Identification Guide to North American Birds, Part I (second edition)
content: Identification Guide to North American Birds, Part I (second edition) by PylePeter with the collaboration of HowellS. N. G. and DeSanteD. F.. 2022. Slate Creek Press, Forest Knolls, California, USA. pp., 318 figures, 81 tables, numerous bar graphs. $90.00 (softcover). ISBN 978-0-9618940-5-4.
